    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the baking tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Add 1 <strong>golden portobello</strong> <strong>mushroom</strong> to each ciabatta base and layer 2 slices of <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> on top</p><p>Add both the <strong>loaded</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>base[s]</strong> and <strong>ciabatta lid[s]</strong> (cut side up) to the other side of the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 5-6 min or until the cheese has melted</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1627993765463-x200.jpg",
