            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pot from the heat and discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>and<strong> </strong>season with a pinch<strong> </strong>of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>minted pea soup</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of boiled water if the soup is looking a little thick!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
