        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sandwich the<strong> loaded</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>base</strong> and <strong>ciabatta lid</strong> together and cut in half diagonally – this is your <strong>cheese & mushroom toastie</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>minted pea soup</strong> in bowls with the <strong>cheese & mushroom toastie</strong> to the side</p><p>Finish with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
